  "designMd": "# Hybrid Design System — Generated by Ditto\n\n> Blended from 3 inspirations\n> Generated on April 9, 2026\n\n## Inspirations\n- [Maxima Therapy | Personalized Support for Neurodivergent Individuals](https://maximatherapy.com/) — weight: 33%\n- [Linear – The system for product development](https://linear.app/) — weight: 33%\n- [App Android su Google Play](https://play.google.com/) — weight: 33%\n\n## Mood Profile\n- **Tono**: Giocoso (-0.5)\n- **Formalità**: Casual (-0.4)\n- **Energia**: Bilanciato (+0.2)\n- **Temperatura**: Bilanciato (0.0)\n- **Densità**: Arioso (-0.5)\n- **Forma**: Bilanciato (-0.3)\n- **Profondità**: Bilanciato (-0.0)\n- **Palette**: Bilanciato (+0.1)\n- **Tipografia**: Espressiva (-0.5)\n- **Movimento**: Bilanciato (+0.3)\n\n## Font Setup\n\n### Fonts Used\n- **Heading**: `ui-sans-serif`\n- **Body**: `Robuck Rounded`\n- **Mono**: `ABC Diatype Rounded Mono`\n\n### CSS Custom Properties\n```css\n:root {\n  --font-heading: 'ui-sans-serif', system-ui, sans-serif;\n  --font-body: 'Robuck Rounded', system-ui, sans-serif;\n  --font-mono: 'ABC Diatype Rounded Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;\n  --font-weight-heading: 600;\n  --font-weight-body: 400;\n}\n```\n\n## Color Palette & Roles\n\n### Primary\n- **Primary** (`#4c911f`): CTAs, interactive elements, brand moments\n- **Secondary** (`#aa3f44`): Supporting accents\n- **Accent** (`#0e8db8`): Decorative highlights\n\n### Surfaces\n- **Background** (`#000000`): Page background\n- **Surface** (`#f8fafc`): Cards, elevated elements\n\n### Text\n- **Primary** (`#ffffff`): Headings, strong labels\n- **Secondary** (`#d0cebf`): Body text, descriptions\n- **Muted** (`#9a9995`): Placeholders, captions\n\n### Semantic\n- **Border** (`#e6d9df`): Dividers, container borders\n- **Success** (`#a7eb98`): Confirmations\n- **Warning** (`#fdcb40`): Caution states\n- **Error** (`#ef4444`): Destructive actions\n\n## Typography Rules\n\n| Role | Font | Weight | Notes |\n|------|------|--------|-------|\n| Display | ui-sans-serif | 600 | Hero headlines |\n| Heading | ui-sans-serif | 600 | Section titles |\n| Body | Robuck Rounded | 400 | Standard text |\n| Mono | ABC Diatype Rounded Mono | 400 | Code, technical |\n\n## Component Stylings\n\n### Buttons\n**Primary**\n- Background: `#4c911f`\n- Text: `#ffffff`\n- Padding: 9px 18px\n- Radius: 14px\n\n**Secondary**\n- Background: transparent\n- Text: `#4c911f`\n- Border: 1px solid `#e6d9df`\n- Radius: 14px\n\n### Cards\n- Background: `#f8fafc`\n- Border: 1px solid `#e6d9df`\n- Radius: 21px\n- Shadow: `0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`\n\n### Inputs\n- Background: `#000000`\n- Border: 1px solid `#e6d9df`\n- Radius: 14px\n- Focus: 1px solid `#4c911f`\n\n## Layout Principles\n\n### Spacing Scale\n- XS: 5px, SM: 9px, MD: 18px\n- LG: 27px, XL: 36px, 2XL: 54px\n\n### Border Radius\n- Small: 7px\n- Medium: 14px\n- Large: 21px\n- Full: 9999px\n\n### Shadows\n- SM: `0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.05)`\n- MD: `0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`\n- LG: `0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)`\n\n## Design Decisions (from Mood Profile)\n\n- **Subtle depth**: Moderate shadows for gentle elevation\n- **Balanced shapes**: Moderate corner rounding\n- **Generous whitespace**: Breathing room between elements\n- **Medium headlines**: Clear hierarchy without overwhelming\n\n## Agent Prompt Guide\n\n### Quick Reference\n- Primary: `#4c911f`, Background: `#000000`\n- Heading: ui-sans-serif @ 600, Body: Robuck Rounded @ 400\n- Radius: 7px / 14px / 21px\n- Spacing: 5px / 9px / 18px / 27px\n\n### CSS Variables (ready to paste)\n```css\n:root {\n  --color-primary: #4c911f;\n  --color-secondary: #aa3f44;\n  --color-accent: #0e8db8;\n  --color-bg: #000000;\n  --color-surface: #f8fafc;\n  --color-text: #ffffff;\n  --color-text-secondary: #d0cebf;\n  --color-text-muted: #9a9995;\n  --color-border: #e6d9df;\n  --color-success: #a7eb98;\n  --color-warning: #fdcb40;\n  --color-error: #ef4444;\n  --radius-sm: 7px;\n  --radius-md: 14px;\n  --radius-lg: 21px;\n  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n  --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n  --shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n```\n",
